    #container
      h1 Ayurvedic Yoga Massage
      p Hi #[span#name -name-]
      p.
        Here are your details for the ayurvedic yoga massage intensive
        training course at #[span#place -place-] on #[span#date -date-].
      // include map!
      // times
      p.
        Prices are &pound;350 for individuals, with a &pound;90 deposit requested two
        weeks before the start date 
        // (so that will be #[span#fortnite -fortnight-]).

      p clicking on any of the buttons below will take you securely to payPal

      a(href='https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_s-xclick&hosted_button_id=B2JF5URJQTFRJ')
        button pay full amount &pound;350
      a(href='https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_s-xclick&hosted_button_id=W4CAJ3UG4HMQ4')
        button pay deposit &pound;90
